#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:49
msgid ""
"Field Monitor is a remote-desktop client designed for the GNOME platform."
msgstr "现场监视器是为 GNOME 平台设计的一款远程桌面客户端。"

#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:53
msgid ""
"It is focused on connecting to virtual machines, but can connect to any "
"server supporting the RDP, SPICE or VNC protocols."
msgstr ""
"其聚焦于与虚拟机的连接，但也可以连接至任何支持 RDP、SPICE 或 VNC 协议的服务"
"器。"

#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:58
msgid ""
"It has support for directly connecting to VMs of the following hypervisors:"
msgstr "支持直接连接至以下管理程序的虚拟机："

#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:62
msgid "Proxmox Virtual Environment"
msgstr "Proxmox 虚拟环境"

#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:64
msgid "QEMU/KVM via libvirt (including GNOME Boxes VMs)"
msgstr "使用 libvirt 的 QEMU/KVM（包括 GNOME Boxes 虚拟机）"

#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:67
msgid ""
"For supported VM hypervisors Field Monitor also offers options to manage the "
"basic power state of VMs, such as starting, stopping, rebooting, etc."
msgstr ""
"现场监视器对支持的虚拟机管理程序提供了管理虚拟机基本电源状态的选项，例如启"
"动、停止、重启等。"

#. Translators: Part of the description of the application in the metainfo.
#: data/de.capypara.FieldMonitor.metainfo.xml.in.in:72
msgid ""
"Additionally, Field Monitor supports opening RDP and Virt Viewer connection "
"files and quickly connecting to RDP, SPICE or VNC servers via URI."
msgstr ""
"另外，现场监视器支持打开 RDP 和 Virt 查看器连接文件以及通过 URI 快速连接至 "
"RDP、SPICE 或 VNC 服务器。"

